2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2!

Until Mon., Mar. 2, at 01:59 UTC

You may purchase the 2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2 up to five times during this campaign to receive a total of 17,500 Gems! You'll also get Chocobo Tail Feathers as a bonus!

These will only be available for purchase until Mon., Mar. 2, at 01:59 UTC, so don't miss out!

2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2


2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2

  • Initial reward: 1,050 Gems, 20 Chocobo Tail Feathers
  • Daily reward: 350 Gems (for 7 days)
  • Total: 3,500 Gems

About Kupocard Mini 2

Upon purchasing either the 2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2, you will receive the initial reward immediately, and the daily reward will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your daily bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh daily reward, you can purchase another 2nd Anniversary Kupocard Mini 2 as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can purchase up to five Kupocards during this period!

* Logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
